    private static class HttpFSFileSystem.HttpFSDataInputStream
extends FilterInputStream
implements org.apache.hadoop.fs.Seekable, org.apache.hadoop.fs.PositionedReadable
    HttpFSServer subclass of the FSDataInputStream.

    This implementation does not support the PositionReadable and Seekable methods.
